{
  "title": "Mighty Kenyan Plum Bake",
  "description": "A traditional Kenyan dish featuring plum sauce and a crumbly texture, often served as a hangover cure, this plant-based friendly bake is cooked in a hot pot vessel.",
  "cuisine": "Kenyan",
  "diet": [
    "plant-based",
